Enough of your soul to keep me trapped
between who I was and who I should be.

38:20.300 --> 38:24.200
I'm nothin' because of you.

38:39.900 --> 38:42.400
You really want it
to end like this?

38:42.400 --> 38:44.200
Sounds like a plan.

38:54.900 --> 38:58.100
Come on, Chief.
Give me a mission.

39:18.100 --> 39:22.600
Really oughta do somethin'
about security.

39:22.600 --> 39:25.200
[Chuckles]
They'll let anybody in here, won't they?

